arStrings.szText: "Have you been taking care of her?"
Since she collapsed in my arms while telling me what happened...to my Vasek (sigh).
I was going to find a Knight Penitent to help her, but she pleaded with me not to. Asked me to hide her, and tell any other priests that came looking that I had not seen her.
Truth be told, I had to wrestle with that. Lying to the Cathedral? Came close to turning her in more than once.
But then I remembered that when I needed help, she did not ask any questions, she was just there, ready to do whatever she could. Well, she deserves the same.
